issue of Details. ; Photo, Canine couture -- Has fashion finally gone to the 
dogs? The cover of the August issue of Details may lead one to think so. ; 
Photo, COLOR, (Orange County Edition) Photographer William Wegman uses dogs as 
sweater models in the August issue of Details. 
</P>
