<P>
Column; Recipe; Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA071990-0043 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 249213 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 19, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
