</P>
<P>
Scott D. Ackerman, Long Beach. Conviction for sexual offenses. License revoked. 
Effective 12/14/89. 
</P>
<P>
Cindy L. Buena-Fe, North Hollywood. Conviction for selling marijuana. License 
revoked. Effective 12/14/89. 
</P>
<P>
Richard Oakley, Los Angeles. Conviction for possession of marijuana for sale. 
License revoked. Effective 12/21/89. 
