LIBRARIES -- ORANGE COUNY; LANGDON WILSON ARCHITECTURE &amp; PLANNING; 
ARCHIVES; NIXON, RICHARD M; POULOS, RICHARD 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA071990-0116 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 249394 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 19, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
