missions, says of the San Fernando Mission: "At least a third of the rooms in 
this building had extensive painted decoration." ; Photo, wall nook MEL MELCON 
/ For The Times; Photo, Norman Neuerburg reconstructed the decor and art of 
Mission San Fernando when it was in their prime. 
</P>
