LIBERATION FRONT; STRIKES; NICARAGUA -- LABOR; NICARAGUA -- ECONOMY; 
PRIVATIZATION; PROPERTY RIGHTS; NICARAGUA -- POLITICS; GOVERNMENT PROPERTY; 
