<TEXT>
<P>
An angry Norm Stewart, denying he misled NCAA investigators looking into 
allegations of wrongdoing in the Missouri basketball program, vowed to carry 
his fight through NCAA hearings and beyond. 
</P>
<P>
"I am willing to assume at this point that the NCAA process will provide me 
with a fair opportunity," Stewart said. "If the NCAA gives me a fair hearing, I 
am confident I will prevail against the allegation. But if the NCAA process 
does not provide me with a fair hearing, I intend to go beyond that process to 
be heard." 
</P>
