<HEADLINE>
<P>
MARIJUANA DEATH SENTENCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, Malaysia 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Yusof Zulti, 27, a clothing vendor, was sentenced to death Wednesday for 
trafficking in 30 ounces of marijuana. 
</P>
