<P>
RESOLUTIONS TOPS QUALIFIERS FOR LOS AL DENIM N DIAMONDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Resolutions beat out 25 quarter horses to emerge as the leading qualifier from 
trials Wednesday night at Los Alamitos for the upcoming $250,000 Denim N 
Diamonds Futurity. 
</P>
<P>
Kip Didericksen piloted Resolutions to a narrow decision over Kipadeucy in the 
second of three time trials Wednesday night while stepping off Los Al's 
400-yard straightaway in 19.95 seconds. 
</P>
<P>
That time stood up as the fastest of the evening, making Resolutions a strong 
pre-race favorite for the July 28 Denim N Diamonds. 
</P>
<P>
Kipadeucy, an Idaho invader supplemented to the trials for $15,000, notched the 
second-fastest qualifying time at 19.97 seconds. 
</P>
<P>
Also winning their trial divisions were Kid O Dash and My Escalon. 
